{{define "about"}}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
{{ template "html-head" headData .CommonPageData "About Bison Explorer"}}
{{template "navbar" . }}
<div class="container mt-2 pb-5">
    <nav class="breadcrumbs mt-0">
        <a href="/" class="breadcrumbs__item no-underline ps-2">
            <span class="homeicon-tags me-1"></span>
            <span class="link-underline">Homepage</span>
        </a>
        <span class="breadcrumbs__item is-active">About</span>
    </nav>
    <div class="row">
        <section style="margin: 0 auto; padding-top: 1rem;">
            <h1 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: #2c3e50;">🐂 About Bison Explorer</h1>
            <!-- Logo -->
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                <img src="/images/logo-bison.png" alt="Bison Explorer Logo" width="300">
                <p style="font-style: italic; color: #666; font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.7rem;">
                    The bison symbolizes growth and upward movement. Our logo depicts a bison embracing the world of
                    blockchain —
                    representing the vision that blockchain and the world will evolve and grow together.
                </p>
            </div>
            <!-- Introduction -->
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 1.3rem;">
                <strong>Bison Explorer</strong> is a powerful and user-friendly blockchain explorer designed to provide
                in-depth, transparent blockchain data for major networks including <strong>Decred (DCR)</strong>,
                <strong>Bitcoin (BTC)</strong>,<strong>Litecoin (LTC)</strong>, and <strong>Monero (XMR)</strong>. We are committed to expanding
                support to more chains in the near future.
            </p>

            <!-- Technical Foundation -->
            <h2 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.5rem; color: #2c3e50;">🌱 Community-Driven Foundation</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                Built upon the robust technical framework of <a href="https://dcrdata.org"
                    style="color: #2980b9; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem !important;">dcrdata</a>, the official explorer by the Decred
                community, Bison Explorer carries forward the values of decentralization, transparency, and open-source
                collaboration. This is a tool crafted by the community, for the community.
            </p>

            <!-- Features -->
            <h2 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.5rem; color: #2c3e50;">📊 Key Features</h2>
            <ul style="font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.3rem; line-height: 1.6; padding-left: 1rem;">
                <li>🔹 Detailed technical views of blocks, transactions, addresses, and mempool states.</li>
                <li>🔹 Live market data including prices, trading volumes, and market capitalization.</li>
                <li>🔹 Visual analytics for transaction activity, hash rate, and coin distribution.</li>
                <li>🔹 <strong>Financial reporting tools tailored for Decred</strong> — enabling deeper ecosystem insights.
                </li>
                <li>🔹 Developer-friendly API access for easy integration with third-party platforms.</li>
                <li>🔹 Responsive, mobile-first design for seamless usage across devices.</li>
            </ul>

            <!-- Vision -->
            <h2 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.5rem; color: #2c3e50;">🚀 Vision for the Future</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                Bison Explorer is more than a data viewer — it is a foundation for blockchain insight and growth. As the
                blockchain space matures, our goal is to evolve with it by supporting more chains, adding advanced
                on-chain analytics, and offering custom dashboards for users, researchers, and developers alike.
            </p>

            <!-- Community Involvement -->
            <h2 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.5rem; color: #2c3e50;">🤝 Join the Journey</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                Bison Explorer is an open and collaborative project. We welcome developers, designers, data analysts,
                and blockchain enthusiasts to contribute and build with us. Let's create the most transparent and
                insightful blockchain explorer together.
            </p>

            <!-- Technical Links -->
            <h2 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.5rem; color: #2c3e50;">🔗 Technical & Community Links</h2>
            <ul style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.6; padding-left: 1rem;">
                <li>🔹 <strong>GitHub:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/chaineco/bisonexplorer"
                        style="color: #2980b9;">https://github.com/chaineco/bisonexplorer</a></li>
                <li>🔹 <strong>X (Twitter):</strong> <a href="https://x.com/bisonexplorer"
                        style="color: #2980b9;">https://x.com/bisonexplorer</a></li>
            </ul>

            <p style="margin-top: 1.8rem; font-size: 1rem; color: #7f8c8d;">
                Bison Explorer – Data transparency. Community-driven. Built for the future of blockchain.
            </p>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>
{{ template "footer" . }}
</body>

</html>
{{end}}